&lt;li&gt;Setting strategic direction of the site based on customer needs and business goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Converting strategic goals into operational tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with graphic designers to create and maintain consistent, branded look and feel across all products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Defining navigational flow and user experience on the site, apps, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Making proposals to senior management regarding implications of proposed plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing and implementing administrative and operational matters ensuring achievement of objectives&lt;/li&gt;
